0.42  2009/09/28 00:00:00
	- rewrite split(m/^/) to split(m/^/m) on any version of perl.
	- fix bug of function Sjis::substr().
	; created by INABA Hitoshi

0.41  2009/09/18 00:00:00
	- add test script.
